! Pin the X server DPI so pango-based fonts (i3 title bars, i3bar) render at a
! consistent size regardless of which monitor is connected at login. Without
! this, Xorg auto-computes DPI from the connected monitor EDID; the 4K HDMI
! panel reports ~154 DPI, which blows up the i3 font at startup.
Xft.dpi: 96
